Streamlit : pip install streamlit
in the correct folder run this command to start the app : streamlit run summarizer.py

Chardet : pip install chardet

Ollama : https://ollama.com
then in cmd : ollama pull mistral (or any model you might prefer).

Whisper : pip install git+https://github.com/openai/whisper.git

ffmpeg : https://www.gyan.dev/ffmpeg/builds/
Download the "essential zip", extract it and drop it in the same folder than your app.
